### Initialize Payment
POST http://localhost:8081/api/payment/init
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "merchantId": "MERCHANT_001",
  "amount": 100.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "stan": "123456",
  "pspTimestamp": 1704412800000
}

###

### Process Card Payment - Valid Visa Card
POST http://localhost:8081/api/payment/process
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "paymentId": "YOUR_PAYMENT_ID_HERE",
  "pan": "4532015112830366",
  "cardHolderName": "John Doe",
  "expiryDate": "12/25",
  "securityCode": "123"
}

###

### Process Card Payment - Valid MasterCard
POST http://localhost:8081/api/payment/process
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "paymentId": "YOUR_PAYMENT_ID_HERE",
